OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1779199898
OL,3,CDisgraced police officer moves to
OL,4,CDevon to set up cocaine network
OL,6,FA disgraced former police officer has
OL,7,Fbeen jailed for helping run a cocaine
OL,8,Fsupply operation between Manchester
OL,9,Fand Devon.
OL,11,FGary Parkinson funded the network and
OL,12,Fused contacts in the North West to
OL,13,Fbuild the supply chain, Exeter Crown
OL,14,FCourt heard.
OL,16,FThe court was told the 45-year-old,
OL,17,Fwho spent 15 years with Greater
OL,18,FManchester Police before moving to
OL,19,FHolsworthy in Devon, began organising
OL,20,Fthe drug line in 2019.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/4
