OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1779199898
OL,3,CDisgraced police officer moves to
OL,4,CDevon to set up cocaine network
OL,6,FCouriers were used to transport half-
OL,7,Fkilo packages of cocaine to Devon.
OL,9,FParkinson was sentenced to six years
OL,10,Fand four months for conspiracy to
OL,11,Fsupply cocaine.
OL,13,FJudge Stephen Climie said the sentence
OL,14,Fwould have been longer, but was
OL,15,Freduced because of a substantial delay
OL,16,Fin the case and Parkinson's serious
OL,17,Fhealth problems.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/4
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
