FL,393,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1779199898
OL,3,CDisgraced police officer moves to
OL,4,CDevon to set up cocaine network
OL,6,FDefence barrister Harry Laidlaw said
OL,7,FParkinson had "sullied his reputation
OL,8,Fwith his decision-making" after
OL,9,Fleaving the force.
OL,11,FHe said a serious quad bike crash in
OL,12,F2018 left him with ongoing health
OL,13,Fissues, but described him as a "man of
OL,14,Fintegrity" who had made a number of
OL,15,Fpoor decisions.
OL,17,FThe judge said Parkinson had lived a
OL,18,Flaw-abiding life and should have
OL,19,Fcontinued to do so after leaving the
OL,20,Fpolice.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/4
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
