OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1779199898
OL,3,CDisgraced police officer moves to
OL,4,CDevon to set up cocaine network
OL,6,FInstead, he played a leading role in
OL,7,Fthe drug operation.
OL,9,FHe also said he was impressed by
OL,10,Freferences submitted on Parkinson's
OL,11,Fbehalf, including from the fire
OL,12,Fservice, which he said did the
OL,13,Fdefendant "great credit."
